{"tid":1395439,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online-防禦裝備須知小補充","createTime":"2019-08-01T17:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:22:13.000Z","uid":35432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"752c7e8f7d64afa6165b4ba86f549152f975e38b","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T17:59:44.000Z","msg":"先擺Source: Dr. Incognito<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/posts/692361607879244?__tn__=K-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDr.Incognito.HK%2Fposts%2F692361607879244%3F__tn__%3DK-R&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFBOHaT3cO7pga%2FagQaCgUd0%3D&h=41ebc767\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Dr.Incognito.HK/posts/692361607879244?__tn__=K-R</a><br />\n最近多咗人新入行做裝修, 想介紹吓職業安全健康知識。<br />\n見到好多新入行嘅朋友買防毒面具買唔到6092x濾罐（按防禦力923=928&gt;926）<br />\n所以唯有用其他組合代替<br />\n其中有一個組合係6006+501+5xxx濾棉<br />\n關於呢度想補充少少嘢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係唔好買5N11濾棉！！！</span></span><br />\n因為N, R, P 講緊個 filter 有幾 oil resistant. 簡單講係啲粒子在油性 aerosol 環境中, 定係就咁空氣中浮浮吓. 齋空氣就用 N, 好似醫院裡面想隔致病源。<br />\n<br />\nN: Not Resistant to Oil --- 過濾最少 95%, 99%, 99.97% (睇 N 後面個數字) 空氣中的浮游粒子. 完全頂唔到油。<br />\nR: Somewhat Resistant to Oil --- 過濾最少 95%, 99%, 99.97% (睇 R 後面個數字) 空氣中的浮游粒子. 會頂到少少油。 <br />\nP: Oil Proof --- 過濾最少 95%, 99%, 99.97% (睇 P 後面個數字) 空氣中的浮游粒子. 強烈頂得順油。<br />\n例如在醫院防止俾人傳染, 用 N 系已夠, 有 SARS 時, 成日講 N95 口罩就係咁解. 至於會 work with 化學品, 例如油漆, 咁就用 P 系最好. 本人從來唔用 R 系, somewhat 頂到啲又頂唔到啲, 都唔知做乜. 重有個 definition 應同時間有關, R 只頂到 8 個鐘, P 就幾倍 (冇記錯係 40 個鐘). 簡單講, 要隔油性嘅, 唔好理 R, 直接用 P 啦.<br />\n<br />\n第二個數字. 95, 99, 100 代表乜呢? 係代表: 隔到幾多個 % 大過 0.3 &mu;m (microns, 10^-6 m, 千分之一個毫米/mm) 直徑嘅粒子.<br />\n<br />\n95: 代表隔到 95% 以上 0.3&mu;m 直徑大的粒子<br />\n99: 代表隔到 99% 以上 0.3&mu;m 直徑大的粒子<br />\n100: 代表隔到 99.97% 以上 0.3&mu;m 直徑大的粒子<br />\n<br />\nN 加埋 95 呢, N95 口罩: 即係一個完全頂唔順油 (即係一有油就失效, 隔唔到咁多、甚至乜都隔唔到), 可隔 95% 以上 0.3&mu;m 直徑大的粒子嘅口罩.<br />\n<br />\n簡單講, 當我唔知面對乜威脅, 做實驗時就揀用 P100, 因唔知 carrier 係油性定非油性. 反正 P 會隔到所有 N 同 R 隔到嘅嘢, tradeoff 係會焗啲.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以5N11係冇防禦力，一定要記得買5P71濾棉!</span></span><br />\n5N11=N95口罩，防禦力=0<br />\n咁多位新入行嘅工友要識得揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66283f384d4a9d19ceb7f3cc42c6019763e0e5d","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"598a910cc58f56f1809539f11aeac0a968e8817c","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f952e6e4734d7697ba8f6185742e6e3ee59f2f21","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"950be948dd5cd4040453e7877ee0d02696177c8f","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:10:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d61a3c49428bca561eb4f0e70c8a5d0e58201e1","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d368936632f982cc3c5333396603597bfab2c241","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f811352fd98fb56508cd781cbe7d3895da7a0301","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:21:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f44d7ca72d141821d2c1dab123ac1e549c8d4475","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T18:39:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3cce480e947f94ced48fb9537787608fb896ac","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:40:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e586f31f9c35ee3d0ff06ac1995782d80434035","tid":1395439,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:49:00.000Z","msg":"Push<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"e69bc0e7dbe5dfdb1eed9d268b6f51ef91f2a42f","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:37:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5428ab6619a2ba502a1584da27408e46deeeccdd","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4495431be46b2c8cdb8c1fec8827b8324aeeb87f","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:36:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f19d23471c18a0e8be5d5c4d83a816baca182b94","tid":1395439,"uid":35432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:22:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}